        <h3>Help</h3>
        <p>

            <a href="https://stackoverflow.com/">Stack Overflow</a> is the premiere Q&A site for developers, enabling the community to vote up best answers, improve on them and comment. If you have a question about Weavy consider posting it there under the [weavy] tag.
        </p>
        <p>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/weavy">See all questions about Weavy</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/ask?tags=weavy">Ask a question about Weavy</a></li>
            </ul>
        </p>
        <p>
            If you have a valid license you can also get priority support by sending an email to support@weavy.com.
        </p>


        <div class="card-deck mt-5">
            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://www.weavy.com/hubfs/faqintro3.svg" class="card-img-top" alt="" style="max-width:200px;align-self: center;">
