                    <h5 class="card-title">Contact us</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Get in touch with us at <a href="mailto:support@@weavy.com">support@@weavy.com</a>. You can also head over to <a href="https://docs.weavy.com">https://docs.weavy.com</a> for all the documentation and tutorials.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <img src="https://www.weavy.com/hubfs/features-collage4.svg" class="card-img-top" alt="" style="max-width: 200px;align-self: center;">
