                    <h5 class="card-title">Try Weavy!</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Want to try out Weavy? No problem, just head over to <a href="https://www.weavy.com/try/app">https://www.weavy.com/try/app</a>. No sign up. No registration. Just do!</p>

                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <div class="text-center"><img src="/img/GitHub-Mark-120px-plus.png" class="card-img-top mt-5" alt="" style="max-width:170px;align-self: center;"></div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">Github</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">Check us out at Github!</p>
